text.text: What is the first step for streamers to get started?
Streamers need to connect their Twitch account to create their profile and get started.
How do streamers set up multiple camera angles?
Streamers can set up multiple camera angles using OBS. They stream their default angle to Twitch and send additional angles to the media server.
What happens when streamers go live?
When streamers go live, their audience will see the main feed while the streamers control the additional camera feeds.
How can viewers join a stream?
Viewers can join a stream by tuning in to their favorite streamers broadcast to see the main camera feed.
What feature allows viewers to switch camera angles?
Viewers can use the interactive interface to choose from multiple camera angles.
How can viewers engage with the content?
Viewers can immerse themselves in the experience and connect with the content by seeing the stream from different angles.
